{"tid":89290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑絲女擸刀兇情敵　紫髮女未驚過舉V字手勢","createTime":"2017-01-21T08:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T09:43:36.000Z","uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4581bfd291c3ccb39ab28548970c76956d8a1c0","tid":89290,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170121/photo/bkn-20170121012129529-0121_00822_001_01p.jpg?20170121162346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170121012129529-0121_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20170121162346&h=58b1d14c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n涉擸刀兇對方的黑絲女，紫髮女舉起V字手勢，黑絲女現任男友(戴頸巾)在場助查。(沈厚錚攝)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旺角深宵上演一幕黑絲女擸刀兇情敵，被兇紫髮女未驚過高舉勝利手勢。昨晚11時許，一名姓楊（18歲）穿黑色絲襪女子，偕同男友途經西洋菜南街132號對開時，巧遇前度男友染紫色頭髮的姓黃（22歲）新歡，兩女疑互看彼此不順眼頓生口角，繼而互相推撞，期間有人突取出一把約10吋利刀向紫髮女子揮舞及恐嚇；途人見狀恐發生血案，隨即報案求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場調查後，將涉案兩名女子拘捕帶署查問，期間染紫髮女子被帶上警車，準備返署受查之際，向在場採訪記者舉起勝利手勢，狀甚「得戚」，警方現以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器及打架將楊女拘捕，而黃女則涉嫌打架被捕。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170121/bkn-20170121012129529-0121_00822_001.html?refer=fn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170121%2Fbkn-20170121012129529-0121_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dfn2&d=vfGss2qHe%2BsvPngnLM%2FXEUsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=bcb7f719\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170121/bkn-20170121012129529-0121_00822_001.html?refer=fn2</a>"},{"pid":"9b4394ff9a2dbf68a046a79edb2ab78e2b4aa93c","tid":89290,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:54:08.000Z","msg":"唔錯唔錯,鍾意黑絲露襪頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8d976dd1ce560513ee4705ed43e03ae1d9020c","tid":89290,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"姓楊（18歲）穿黑色絲襪女子 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset